    {
        "content": "<p>The relation between ordinals in different universes might become more clear keeping this theorem in mind: <code>Ordinal.{u}</code> embeds as an initial segment of <code>Ordinal.{max u v}</code>, and this embedding preserves all arithmetic operations.</p>",
        "id": 494516937,
        "sender_full_name": "Violeta Hernández",
        "timestamp": 1737205113
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Btw I only recently added <code>Ordinal.omega</code>, so there might be some missing API; if such let me know!</p>",
